Subject: Secunia Research: Xpdf JBIG2 Symbol Dictionary Buffer Overflow Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 17/04/2009

    - Xpdf JBIG2 Symbol Dictionary Buffer Overflow Vulnerability -

